{"tid":2326364,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【退位之後新搞作】Meghan Markle 大力投資植物製嘅奶粉","createTime":"2020-12-15T09:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T11:23:01.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c92891d6cdfc7d28c8bbffaa3fad21cfbe673a7","tid":2326364,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:32:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.adaymag.com/2020/12/15/meghan-markle-first-public-personal-investment.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaymag.com%2F2020%2F12%2F15%2Fmeghan-markle-first-public-personal-investment.html&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=6e7f6358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.adaymag.com/2020/12/15/meghan-markle-first-public-personal-investment.html</a>"},{"pid":"c3011d367c0cd75a975b6bf802891a4efefb322c","tid":2326364,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"退位後的新事業版圖：Meghan Markle 低調投資，默默賣起這項「產品」<br />\n<br />\n回顧今年初，Prince Harry 和 Meghan Markle 在無預警宣布退位後，遇到了不少爭議與批評。失去皇室光環加持的他們，接下來也必須思考如何在經濟獨立的道路上，找到新的收入。近日，Meghan Markle 低調地投資一間公司，拓展了新的事業版圖，引發外界討論。<br />\n<br />\nMeghan Markle 投資食品公司<br />\n「我很喜歡而且吃起來很健康」<br />\n<br />\n根據美國雜誌《Fortune》（財星）的報導，退位後，Meghan Markle 第一項公開的投資事業，鎖定了美國食品公司 &ldquo;Clevr Blends&rdquo;，該公司專門製作「植物奶」沖泡粉，取代傳統的「牛奶」成分，讓喝起來的口感更豐富、濃郁，並提供咖啡、抹茶、奶茶等多種口味。<br />\n<br />\nMeghan 看準的，不僅是「植物奶」在未來的趨勢，也是為了力挺「女性」。專訪中，她表示：「這項投資是為了支持一位熱情的女企業家，在建立事業前，優先考量到如何凝聚社區共識。我很榮幸投資 Hannah Mendoza（Clevr Blends 的創辦人兼執行長）的產品。」"},{"pid":"2d10479f5a4ee04d8b090b95a640a6cb6550ee8b","tid":2326364,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:34:58.000Z","msg":"「我個人很喜歡這些產品，而且就整體而言，食品的成份也對人體有益。我相信她，我也相信她的公司。」 Meghan 早在 2017 年，已經接觸了該品牌。當她喝了該公司製作的植物奶沖泡飲，倍感喜愛，並在了解品牌的創立故事後，成了她退位之後拓展事業的新版圖。<br />\n<br />\nMeghan 不為品牌拍廣告<br />\n卻懂得如何操作「宣傳」能力<br />\n<br />\nClevr Blends 原本是一家咖啡快閃店，沒有固定的實體店面。當初，創辦人開著多功能休旅車，在街道上販賣咖啡與自家產品，隨著越來越多人喜歡，商品慢慢地開始受到大家關注，更陸續在商店裡上架。如今，在 Meghan 的投資之下，也有了更多「曝光」的管道。<br />\n<br />\n然而，Meghan 不走親自代言廣告的宣傳方式。打開 Clevr Blends 的官方網站與社群平台，完全沒有看見 Meghan Markle 的身影。她似乎有意與品牌保持一定的「距離」，增添一抹神秘感，讓品牌低調地散發商品的特質與魅力，再吸引有興趣的消費者前來了解與購買。<br />\n<br />\n稍早，Oprah Winfrey 分享一則影片，表示收到了來自 &ldquo;M&rdquo; 的聖誕禮物，裡面裝著的，就是 Clevr Blends 植物奶產品系列。雖然過程沒有提及是 Meghan Markle 投資的，但能在近兩千萬追蹤者的 Instagram 頁面上曝光，並傳遞對該產品的喜愛，已是最成功的宣傳。"},{"pid":"e4298d19dfb69f07d864eca6a09cf0b4ac7355c8","tid":2326364,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"Google 一下 ：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.newsapi.com.au/image/v1/fd61c15d016619ce9251d2315cc00a2d?width=650\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.newsapi.com.au%2Fimage%2Fv1%2Ffd61c15d016619ce9251d2315cc00a2d%3Fwidth%3D650&h=1f1cfe79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係素食撚 ....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b849eb653319225b4a4d2e122062036aeb9b8f","tid":2326364,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"臭閪一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a47693993afecd32731def7bd321a1b5b6dd42f","tid":2326364,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8b849eb653319225b4a4d2e122062036aeb9b8f","tid":2326364,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"臭閪一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:38:50.000Z","msg":"就係知道個朵臭<br />\n所以開水喉投資隻野<br />\n都保持距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14dfd5c02885f70c7c62b01d442c5a7ff724a4a","tid":2326364,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"植物奶（素食撚）<br />\n女性企業家（女權）<br />\n<br />\n兩樣野都係連登仔最閪憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c062fffb03b999deed8ac89f7d668375013a554b","tid":2326364,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:23:01.000Z","msg":"素食本身無問題，咪撚過晒火就得"}]}